---
title: Smart Beyond Meat®  and Mushroom Stew with Potatoes and Spinach
description: This hearty dinner has all the flavours of a traditional stew, but lightened up. Beyond Meat®, potatoes, thyme, mushrooms and spinach are featured in this dish that's sure to warm you up from the inside out.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-beyond-meat-et-de-champignons-92d54a91.jpg
